No! Stop it! What are you doing? Idiot! Let me do it!

9
00:05:24,292 --> 00:05:26,500
运行……快去找个人。
Run... run and find someone.

10
00:05:31,333 --> 00:05:35,542
去……去,快。快!
Go... go, quick. Quick!

11
00:05:44,667 --> 00:05:46,792
你还在等什么?
What the hell are you waiting for?

12
00:05:48,250 --> 00:05:51,000
快点!走吧!
Hurry Up! Go!

13
00:06:02,167 --> 00:06:06,917
你还在等什么?你没看见我快死了吗?
What are you waiting for? Don't you see I'm dying?

14
00:06:09,917 --> 00:06:12,000
你听不见我说话吗?
Can't you hear me?

15
00:06:29,667 --> 00:06:31,917
看看有多少血。
Look how much blood.

16
00:06:35,542 --> 00:06:37,958
