进车里，安静点。闭上你的嘴。
Get in the car and be quiet. Keep your mouth shut.

26
00:08:47,875 --> 00:08:51,542
安静!不要害怕。我们不会对你做什么。
Quiet! Don't be afraid. We won't do anything to you.

27
00:08:51,583 --> 00:08:54,583
别伤害他。
Don't hurt him.

28
00:09:01,125 --> 00:09:03,917
给他戴上眼罩。
Get a blindfold for him.

29
00:09:27,042 --> 00:09:29,708
我们快点吧。
Let's hurry up.

30
00:09:30,292 --> 00:09:32,542
不要害怕。
Don't be afraid.

31
00:09:32,583 --> 00:09:35,750
嘿!他什么都能看见。来吧，把他的眼罩弄平。
Hey! He can see everything. C'mon, set his blindfold right.

32
00:09:36,417 --> 00:09:38,750
好的。快。我们走吧。
Ok. Quick. Let's go.

33
00:09:41,250 --> 00:09:45,000
来吧。快。小声点。帮助我。快点。
C'mon. Quick. Keep the noise down. Help me. Hurry up.

34
00:09:48,042 --> 00:09:50,833
就像爬到各各他一样。-闭嘴，混蛋。
It's just like climbing to Golgotha. - Shut up, asshole.

35
00:09:56,750 --> 00:09:58,417
把门关上。
Close the door.

36
00:09:58,417 --> 00:10:00,833
别紧张。
Just take it easy.

37
00:10:02,167 --> 00:10:04,750
别担心。
Don't worry.

38
00:13:08,917 --> 00:13:10,583
但是你们有祸了，大地和海洋!< / i >
