39
00:13:10,583 --> 00:13:15,958
你悲伤的时刻到了!当魔鬼降临到你身上时……</i>
<i>Your grieving time has come! As the Devil has come down to you...</i>

40
00:13:15,958 --> 00:13:18,417
…他非常愤怒，因为他知道他只有很短的时间了
...in <i>great fury, since he knows he has but a short time.</i>

41
00:13:18,917 --> 00:13:22,000
当龙看到自己被扔到地上时
<i>When the dragon saw that it had been thrown down to the earth...</i>

42
00:13:22,208 --> 00:13:24,833
…如果我开始追求那个女人
...it <i>started to pursue the woman...</i>

43
00:13:25,167 --> 00:13:27,083
<我>…这个男孩是谁生的
<i>...who had given birth to the male child.</i>

44
00:13:29,458 --> 00:13:32,208
我喜欢你，你知道的。我爱你们所有人。
I like you, you know. I love you all.

45
00:13:32,208 --> 00:13:35,500
我喜欢你说话的方式。我喜欢你的穿着。
I like the way you talk. I like the way you dress.

46
00:13:35,792 --> 00:13:40,875
他也不错。但是我想说……他还不完整。
He's not bad too. But I'd say...he's not complete.

47
00:13:42,042 --> 00:13:45,167
他还不完整。
He's not complete.

48
00:13:56,292 --> 00:13:58,708
在这里。
Here.

49
00:13:59,917 --> 00:14:02,625
好的。他现在看起来好多了。
Ok. He looks better now.

50
00:14:02,708 --> 00:14:05,417
我现在更喜欢他了。更多!
I like him more now. Much more!

51
00:14:05,542 --> 00:14:08,458
你想要牧师?他来了，等着你。
You wanted a priest? Here he is, ready for you.

52
00:14:08,625 --> 00:14:11,125
你现在必须付清你的赌注。
You have to pay off your bet now.

53
00:14:11,250 --> 00:14:14,583
谁把他打扮得像个牧师?
Who has dressed him like a priest?

54
00:14:14,625 --> 00:14:18,250
他揭开了第六印，于是发生了大地震
<i>He broke open the sixth seal and there was a great earthquake.</i>

55
00:14:18,458 --> 00:14:21,125
