...the <i>whole moon became like blood. The stars in the sky...</i>

57
00:14:25,917 --> 00:14:29,500
<我>…像未成熟的无花果被摇散一样落在地上
<i>...fell to the earth like unripe figs shaken loose...</i>

58
00:14:29,583 --> 00:14:32,333
<i>…在强风中从树上掉下来。</i>
<i>...from the tree in a strong wind.</i>

59
00:14:41,250 --> 00:14:44,833
你是谁?是谁?
Who is this? Who is?

60
00:14:44,917 --> 00:14:49,292
<i>第一个，最后一个，活着的那个。</i>
<i>The first one, the last one, the one who lives.</i>

61
00:15:02,875 --> 00:15:04,958
你还需要我吗?
Do you still need me?

62
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:08,833
