64
00:15:20,167 --> 00:15:22,625
不。现在我没心情了。
No. Now I'm not in the mood anymore.

65
00:15:22,750 --> 00:15:25,875
我不想!我不再要了!
I don't want to! I no longer want!

66
00:15:27,708 --> 00:15:33,208
在那时候，人要求死，却寻不著死
<i>During that time men will seek death but will not find it.</i>

67
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:37,750
他们渴望死亡，但死亡会逃离他们
<i>They will long to die but death will escape them.</i>

68
00:15:37,833 --> 00:15:43,000
蝗虫的样子就像准备打仗的马
<i>The appearance of the locusts was like that of horses ready for battle.</i>

69
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:46,875
在他们的头上，他们戴着看起来像金冠的东西
<i>On their heads they wore what looked like crowns of gold...</i>

70
00:15:46,958 --> 00:15:49,750
<我>…他们的脸就像人类的脸
<i>...and their faces were like human faces.</i>

71
00:15:50,417 --> 00:15:52,625
他们的头发就像女人的头发
<i>And they had hair like women's hair...</i>

72
00:15:52,708 --> 00:15:55,500
<我>…他们的牙齿就像狮子的牙齿
<i>...and their teeth were like lions' teeth.</i>

73
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:58,583
他们的胸部像铁胸甲
<i>They had chests like iron breastplates.</i>

74
00:15:58,917 --> 00:16:05,042
[i bbb]它们翅膀的声音就像许多马车的声音
<i>The sound of their wings was like the one of many horse-drawn chariots...</i>

75
00:16:05,167 --> 00:16:07,708
<我>…冲进战场。他们有像蝎子一样的尾巴
<i>...racing into battle. They had tails like scorpions.</i>

76
00:16:07,958 --> 00:16:12,417
它们的尾巴有能力伤害人类长达5个月之久
<i>With their tails they had power to harm people for five months.</i>

77
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:15,208
<i bbb >他们有深渊天使作他们的王
<i>They had as their king the angel of the abyss...</i>

78
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:17,500
<我>…他的名字在希伯来语里是亚巴顿。< / i > . .
<i>...whose name in Hebrew is Abaddon.</i> ..

79
00:16:17,583 --> 00:16:20,542
<我>…在希腊语中是Apollyon.</i>
<i>...and in Greek Apollyon.</i>

80
00:16:22,208 --> 00:16:24,917
说得好!
Well said!

81
00:16:26,583 --> 00:16:31,000
你至少可以为自己辩护或者寻求帮助，神父。
You could have defended yourself at least or asked for help, Father.

82
00:16:31,167 --> 00:16:33,125
或者试图逃跑。
Or tried to escape.

83
00:16:33,250 --> 00:16:35,833
你为什么不这么做，神父?
Why didn't you do that, Father?

84
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:41,958
你为什么不这么做?
Why didn't you do that?

85
00:16:49,792 --> 00:16:52,000
我很抱歉。
I'm sorry.

86
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:54,958
我不知道。
I didn't know.

87
00:17:03,625 --> 00:17:06,000
现在把鞋穿上。它是凉的。
Wear your shoes now. It's cold.

88
00:17:07,417 --> 00:17:09,958
我在那里谁也不认识。
I didn't know anybody there.

89
00:17:10,708 --> 00:17:13,750
但刚开始的时候很有趣。
But it was fun when it started.

90
00:17:14,667 --> 00:17:18,000
但是你被冻住了。来吧，我们跑一跑。
But you're frozen. C'mon, let's make a run.

91
00:17:41,167 --> 00:17:44,000
你现在感觉好点了吗?——是的。
Do you feel better now? - Yes.

92
00:17:44,083 --> 00:17:46,958
我有点累了。
I'm a little bit tired.

93
00:17:47,875 --> 00:17:50,125
你要相信我，我很抱歉……
You have to believe me, I'm so sorry for...

94
00:17:50,333 --> 00:17:52,750
哦，不，毕竟是我的错。
Oh no, it's my fault, after all.

95
00:17:52,833 --> 00:17:55,500
我真不知道我为什么会在这里。
I really don't know why I've found myself around here.

96
00:17:55,583 --> 00:17:57,833
也许你想一个人待着。
Perhaps you wanted to be alone.

97
00:17:59,208 --> 00:18:01,500
午夜时分你扔掉了什么?
What did you throw away around midnight?

98
00:18:01,500 --> 00:18:06,708
哦,没什么。人们仍然坚持向窗外扔东西。
Oh, nothing. People still insist on throwing stuff out the windows.

99
00:18:06,708 --> 00:18:11,958
他们相信明年的情况会好得多。
They're convinced that things will go better and much better next year.

100
00:18:13,250 --> 00:18:15,250
反正我也不相信。
Well, I don't believe it, anyway.

101
00:18:19,458 --> 00:18:22,833
嘿，看那儿!-是牧师!
Hey, look there! - It's a priest!

102
00:18:24,667 --> 00:18:27,667
Ring-a-ring-0“玫瑰…
Ring-a-ring-0'-roses...

103
00:18:40,250 --> 00:18:43,458
我希望这对你来说真的是更好的一年。
I hope that it will be really a better year for you.

104
00:18:45,292 --> 00:18:49,000
我能对牧师许什么愿呢?
What can I wish for a priest?

105
00:18:49,833 --> 00:18:52,083
回去找你的朋友吧。
Get back to your friends.

106
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:56,542
我为什么要这么做?
Why should I?

107
00:18:58,500 --> 00:19:01,875
现在我只是不想。
Now I just don't want to.

108
00:19:14,833 --> 00:19:17,000
我的兄弟姐妹们，在庆祝神圣的奥秘之前……
My brothers and sisters, before celebrating the sacred mysteries...

109
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:19,042
…让我们想起我们的罪。
...let's call to mind our sins.

110
00:19:19,125 --> 00:19:21,750
我向全能的上帝忏悔，也向你忏悔……
I confess to almighty God, and to you...

111
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:24,333
…我的兄弟姐妹们，我因自己的过错而有罪……
...my brothers and sisters, that I've sinned through my own fault...

112
00:19:24,417 --> 00:19:26,958
…在我的思想中，在我的言语中，在我的所作所为中……
...in my thoughts and in my words, in what I've done...

113
00:19:26,958 --> 00:19:28,500
…还有我没能做到的事
...and in what I've failed to do.

114
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:31,292
我请求圣母玛利亚，永远的处女，所有的天使……
And I ask blessed Mary, ever virgin, all the angels...

115
00:19:31,292 --> 00:19:34,417
…圣徒们，还有你们，我的兄弟姐妹们，请为我祈祷。
...and saints, and you, my brothers and sisters, to pray for me.

116
00:22:27,917 --> 00:22:31,000
愿主与你们同在。-你也一样。
The Lord be with you. - And also with you.

117
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,292
让我们祈祷吧。
Let us pray.

118
00:22:32,375 --> 00:22:34,458
主啊，我们把你仆人夏娃的灵魂托付给你……
We commend to you, Lord, the soul of your servant Eve...

119
00:22:34,500 --> 00:22:37,083
…这样她就能活在你的身体里…
...so that she can live on in you after this life...

120
00:22:37,083 --> 00:22:40,333
…她因人性的弱点而犯下的罪恶……
...and the sins she committed through human weakness...

121
00:22:40,333 --> 00:22:42,333
…可以被你的仁慈所宽恕。
...can be forgiven by your mercy.

122
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:45,583
借着我们的主耶稣基督。——阿门。
Through our Lord, Jesus Christ. - Amen.

123
00:22:57,042 --> 00:22:59,875
我已经叫你不要再来了。
I had asked you not to come again.

124
00:23:01,167 --> 00:23:03,667
但我必须见到你。
But I had to see you.

125
00:23:05,000 --> 00:23:07,708
我永远地离开了他们。
I left them forever.

126
00:23:07,750 --> 00:23:10,250
为什么?
Why?

127
00:23:11,667 --> 00:23:14,458
我讨厌他们所有人。
I hate them all.

128
00:23:16,083 --> 00:23:18,708
我想要忘记。
I want to forget.

129
00:23:25,542 --> 00:23:28,500
逃跑有什么意义?
What's the point of running away?

130
00:23:28,625 --> 00:23:31,750
你永远也逃不掉了。从来没有
You will be never able to run away. Never

131
00:23:31,792 --> 00:23:34,125
你无处可去。
There's no place where you can go.

132
00:23:34,208 --> 00:23:37,083
你没有希望了。
There's no hope for you.

133
00:23:37,500 --> 00:23:39,875
他们伤害了你这么多。
They have hurt you so much.

134
00:23:39,917 --> 00:23:42,375
他们夺走了你的一切。
They have taken everything from you.

135
00:23:42,417 --> 00:23:44,750
有一天，为了拯救你自己…
And one day, to save yourself...

136
00:23:44,750 --> 00:23:47,250
…也许你会被迫杀人。
...maybe you'll be forced to kill.

137
00:23:47,833 --> 00:23:50,500
杀死……
To kill...

138
00:24:34,042 --> 00:24:36,667
我看到她进来过。
I've seen she's got in here.

139
00:24:36,708 --> 00:24:38,875
嘿，你在干什么?我们在找你。
Hey, what are you doing? We were looking for you.

140
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:41,125
来吧，我们走吧。-回到我们身边。这是一座教堂。
C'mon, let's go away. - Come back to us. This is a church.

141
00:24:41,125 --> 00:24:44,250
你不知道吗?来吧!我们走吧。-不过她喝醉了。
Don't you know? C'mon! Let's go. - She's drunk, though.

142
00:24:44,250 --> 00:24:46,917
她喝得烂醉如泥。你喝醉了。——不!
She's dead drunk. You're drunk. - No!

143
00:24:46,917 --> 00:24:50,542
你进不去，你喝醉了。停!——不!别烦我!
You can't get in, you're drunk. Stop! - No! Leave me alone!

144
00:24:50,958 --> 00:24:53,458
走开!
Go away!

145
00:25:19,500 --> 00:25:23,458
你所爱的人死后，我埋葬了他们。
I buried your loved ones when they died.

146
00:25:24,250 --> 00:25:27,000
你儿子出生时我给他们施了洗。
I baptized your sons when they were born.

147
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:30,458
当你们说彼此相爱时，我加入了你们的婚姻。
I joined you in marriage when you said you love each other.

148
00:25:30,500 --> 00:25:35,125
我听到了你的罪恶，却无法帮助你。
And I heard your sins, without being able to help you.

149
00:25:36,667 --> 00:25:41,458
今天……我试着向你忏悔。
Today...I've tried to confess to you.

150
00:25:42,250 --> 00:25:45,250
但我不知道我能不能做到。
But I don't know if I could do it.

151
00:25:45,833 --> 00:25:48,583
我不知道这是否可能。
I don't know if it's possible.

152
00:25:49,625 --> 00:25:52,375
我想告诉你关于我的一切……
I wanted to tell you everything about me...

153
00:25:53,083 --> 00:25:57,833
…我觉得自己不配听到你的罪恶。
...and how I'm feeling unworthy of hearing your sins.

154
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:04,000
我是如何无力履行我的职责。
How I've been powerless to perform my duties.

155
00:26:07,500 --> 00:26:13,458
我的感受……我还没决定我的任务有多重要。
How I've felt...been undecided about the importance of my mission.

156
00:26:15,917 --> 00:26:20,458
我希望我的最后一次布道会有所不同。
I was hoping that this last sermon of mine would be different.

157
00:26:22,375 --> 00:26:26,542
今天我要向你们告别，因为我要去一个新的教区了。
Today I say goodbye to you, as I will go to a new parish.

158
00:26:27,625 --> 00:26:30,000
我已经做了这个决定……
I've taken this decision...

159
00:26:30,042 --> 00:26:33,083
…因为我认为这样对你比较好……
...as I think it's better for you...

160
00:26:34,625 --> 00:26:37,333
…对我来说也是。
...and for me.

161
00:26:38,750 --> 00:26:43,625
出于谦卑，我真的请求你试着理解我的话……
In all humility, I really ask you to try to understand my words...

162
00:26:43,792 --> 00:26:46,458
…并原谅我。
...and to forgive me.

163
00:26:47,125 --> 00:26:51,250
我希望我值得你的理解……
I hope I've deserved your comprehension...

164
00:26:51,500 --> 00:26:55,125
…感谢我们在一起这么多年。
...for all the years we have been together.

165
00:26:57,417 --> 00:27:00,667
我想我找不到合适的词来形容……
I think I'm unable to find the right words...

166
00:27:00,750 --> 00:27:06,500
…在福音里…而我在自己身上找不到。
...in the gospel...and I can't find them in myself.

167
00:27:09,500 --> 00:27:12,292
我知道我该说什么。
I know what I should say.

168
00:27:12,292 --> 00:27:16,792
但我也知道……我永远不会说的。
But I also know that... I will never say it.

169
00:27:21,667 --> 00:27:25,292
今天我决定离开你，因为……
Today I've decided to leave you because...

170
00:27:25,750 --> 00:27:29,292
…我害怕我的责任。
...I'm afraid of my responsibility.

171
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:34,875
因为我意识到我帮不了你。
Because I realize that I can't help you.

172
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:43,458
因为我给不了你你给我的爱。
Because I couldn't give you the same love you gave me.

173
00:27:45,792 --> 00:27:49,458
我想说出真相，但我失败了。
I wanted to tell the truth but I failed.

174
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:53,833
我试着跟你谈谈基督教的爱……
I tried to talk to you about Christian love...

175
00:27:53,875 --> 00:27:56,500
…但我的话听起来很假。
...but my words sounded fake.

176
00:27:56,542 --> 00:27:59,125
我为此感到羞愧。
And I felt ashamed of that.

177
00:27:59,792 --> 00:28:02,958
就像你对自己的罪恶感到羞耻一样。
Just like you feel ashamed of your sins.

178
00:28:04,333 --> 00:28:06,958
当牧师可不容易。
It's not easy to be a priest.

179
00:28:09,792 --> 00:28:13,917
在一个掺假的世界里，这并不容易……
It's not easy in a world where things are adulterated...

180
00:28:13,958 --> 00:28:19,917
…真相被扭曲了。
...and the truth is distorted.

181
00:28:21,042 --> 00:28:24,083
这就是为什么今天的人们……
That's just why today people...

182
00:28:24,375 --> 00:28:29,500
…当然，还有你们大多数人，你们简单、坦率、忠诚……
...and also most of you, of course, who are simple, frank and faithful...

183
00:28:29,500 --> 00:28:32,458
…被怀疑所麻痹。
...are paralyzed by doubt.

184
00:28:34,333 --> 00:28:39,458
怀疑是人类本性和生活的一部分。
Doubting is part of human nature and life by now.

185
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:45,250
每个人都必须避免孤独……
Everyone has to avoid loneliness...

186
00:28:46,583 --> 00:28:49,042
…和其他人在一起。
...and to be together with the others.

187
00:28:49,042 --> 00:28:51,458
因为孤独的人对任何事都有怀疑。
Because a lonely man has doubts about anything.

188
00:28:51,583 --> 00:28:54,083
甚至关于上帝。
Even about God.

189
00:28:54,542 --> 00:28:57,458
所以很难帮助他。
And so it's hard to help him.

190
00:28:58,167 --> 00:29:01,500
当一个人失去了自己的信仰……
When a man loses his own faith...

191
00:29:01,958 --> 00:29:04,750
…他甚至不相信自己。
...he doesn't even believe in himself.

192
00:29:06,042 --> 00:29:08,458
他很快就变得虚弱了。
He becomes weak soon...

193
00:29:08,667 --> 00:29:10,917
…他的肉体控制了他。
...as his flesh takes control.

194
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:13,708
他迷了路，不知不觉中……
He loses his way and without knowing it...

195
00:29:13,708 --> 00:29:17,958
…走到哪儿也去不了，还迷路了。
...takes the road to nowhere and gets lost.

196
00:29:24,167 --> 00:29:26,542
我知道，这些只是混淆的词语。
These are only confused words, I know.

197
00:29:26,667 --> 00:29:29,875
我试着告诉你我的真实感受。
I've tried to tell you what I'm really feeling.

198
00:29:30,083 --> 00:29:34,208
现在我都不知道我这么做是为你好还是为我好。
And now I don't even know if I did it for my or your good.

199
00:29:35,542 --> 00:29:39,167
就是这样。请原谅我。原谅我。
That's it. Forgive me, please. Forgive me.

200
00:30:02,958 --> 00:30:05,458
在这里见到我你感到惊讶吗?
Are you surprised to see me here?

201
00:30:08,167 --> 00:30:10,542
我都不知道……
I don't even know...

202
00:30:12,292 --> 00:30:15,292
…我为什么回来，为什么回来
...why I'm back and what's for.

203
00:30:16,958 --> 00:30:19,875
我只知道我累了……
I only know I'm tired...

204
00:30:20,250 --> 00:30:25,875
…厌倦了逃避。我总是这么做。它总是没用的。
...tired of running away. I always do it. It's always useless.

205
00:30:26,167 --> 00:30:28,917
但你能理解我，不是吗?
But you can understand me, can't you?

206
00:30:30,625 --> 00:30:34,417
因为你也做不到。
Because you can't make it either.

207
00:30:34,583 --> 00:30:38,917
你说对了。你承认了。
You said it. You admitted it.

208
00:30:39,458 --> 00:30:42,375
我太累了。
I'm so tired.

209
00:30:42,417 --> 00:30:44,750
我喝醉了，你看到了吗?
And I'm drunk, you see?

210
00:30:44,875 --> 00:30:47,208
我很困惑。
I'm so confused.

211
00:30:47,292 --> 00:30:49,000
然后我来到这里……
Then I came here...

212
00:30:49,083 --> 00:30:51,292
…我听了你的布道
...and I heard your sermon.

213
00:30:51,375 --> 00:30:55,583
我听了。我得到了。
I listened to it. And I got it.

214
00:30:56,750 --> 00:31:01,042
但那不是牧师的布道。
But it wasn't a sermon by a priest.

215
00:31:01,125 --> 00:31:03,208
你知道为什么吗?
Do you know why?

216
00:31:03,333 --> 00:31:07,375
因为你不是牧师。
Because you're not a priest.

217
00:31:07,417 --> 00:31:11,083
你只是半个牧师，不完全是。
You're only half a priest, not entirely.

218
00:31:14,083 --> 00:31:17,125
我说得对吗，父亲?
Am I right, Father?

219
00:31:17,208 --> 00:31:19,750
不要和我争论……
And do not argue with me...

220
00:31:19,833 --> 00:31:22,875
…因为你得听我的。
...because you have to listen to me.

221
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:26,958
你必须这么做，即使你不想这么做。
You have to, even if you don't want to.

222
00:31:27,500 --> 00:31:31,792
因为那是你的工作。
Because that's your job.

223
00:31:35,125 --> 00:31:38,500
倾听每个人的意见。每一个人。
Listening to everyone. Everyone.

224
00:31:40,750 --> 00:31:42,875
多么荒谬的……
How absurd...

225
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:45,500
…和无用……
...and useless...

226
00:31:45,500 --> 00:31:49,083
多么愚蠢……
How stupid...

227
00:31:51,708 --> 00:31:54,542
我在这里做什么?
What am I doing here?

228
00:31:54,583 --> 00:31:57,458
你能告诉我我会变成什么样子吗?
Can you tell me what will become of me?

229
00:31:57,542 --> 00:31:58,833
我会喝酒。
I can drink.

230
00:31:58,917 --> 00:32:02,042
我很擅长喝酒，你知道的。
Well, I'm good at drinking, you know.

231
00:32:02,250 --> 00:32:04,917
然后和我喜欢的人上床。
Then I sleep with whoever I like.

232
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:09,500
我和我喜欢的人上床。
And I sleep with whoever I like.

233
00:32:10,292 --> 00:32:12,958
怎么了，神父?你感到震惊吗?
What's up, Father? Are you shocked?

234
00:32:13,875 --> 00:32:16,625
没有爱我活不下去。
I can't live without love.

235
00:32:16,792 --> 00:32:19,833
我去不了。
I can't make it.

236
00:32:19,917 --> 00:32:22,042
即使我了解男人。
Even if I know men.

237
00:32:22,083 --> 00:32:25,250
我确实认识他们。
And I do know them.

238
00:32:27,250 --> 00:32:30,917
我不是妻子……
I'm not a wife...

239
00:32:31,042 --> 00:32:34,208
…我不是妓女……
...I'm not a whore...

240
00:32:34,250 --> 00:32:36,750
…我什么都没有。
...I'm nothing.

241
00:32:44,417 --> 00:32:46,875
是的，你说得对。
Yes, you're right.

242
00:32:47,167 --> 00:32:48,875
我是对的。
And I'm right.

243
00:32:49,042 --> 00:32:50,625
每个人都是对的。
And everyone's right.

244
00:32:50,708 --> 00:32:53,250
我在旋转自己…
And I'm spinning myself...

245
00:32:53,250 --> 00:32:56,000
…就像风车一样。
...like a pinwheel.

246
00:32:56,125 --> 00:32:58,458
我已经不知道该如何停下来了。
I no longer know how to stop.

247
00:32:58,708 --> 00:33:00,958
谁能阻止我?
How can one stop me?

248
00:33:01,042 --> 00:33:03,417
只能靠喝酒。
Only by drinking.

249
00:33:03,833 --> 00:33:06,250
我可能会自杀。
I might try to kill myself.

250
00:33:10,125 --> 00:33:12,542
你觉得呢?
Well, what do you think?

251
00:33:15,417 --> 00:33:16,708
你不相信我。
You don't believe me.

252
00:33:16,833 --> 00:33:19,792
你不想相信我!
You don't want to believe me!

253
00:33:19,875 --> 00:33:23,083
你听过多少次这样的忏悔，神父?
How many confessions like this have you listened to, Father?

254
00:33:23,125 --> 00:33:27,208
有多少绝望的，小气的，伪装者的忏悔?
How many confessions by desperate, petty, pretender people?

255
00:33:27,458 --> 00:33:29,750
你为什么要听他们的?
Why are you listening to them?

256
00:33:29,875 --> 00:33:32,417
是的，当然，他们需要帮助。
Yes, sure, they need help.

257
00:33:32,583 --> 00:33:35,625
你说得对，但我和他们不一样。我变得更糟。
You're right but I'm not like them. I'm worse.

258
00:33:35,708 --> 00:33:37,625
你知道为什么吗?
And you know why?

259
00:33:37,792 --> 00:33:40,625
因为我什么都不在乎。
Because I care about nothing.

260
00:33:40,708 --> 00:33:42,417
这不是忏悔。
This is not a confession.

261
00:33:42,583 --> 00:33:44,750
这些都不是我的罪。
And these are not my sins.

262
00:33:44,875 --> 00:33:46,708
这些都是别人犯的罪。
These are the sins by the others.

263
00:33:46,750 --> 00:33:49,208
那是他们的狗屎。
That's their shit.

264
00:33:53,375 --> 00:33:55,458
是的,当然。
Yes, sure.

265
00:33:55,708 --> 00:33:58,375
你也是个男人。
You're a man too.

266
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:01,875
一个和其他男人一样的男人。
A man like all the other men.

267
00:34:03,708 --> 00:34:06,917
一个穿着黑色衣服的小个子男人……
A little man dressed in black...

268
00:34:09,792 --> 00:34:11,875
…他什么都不懂。
...who understands nothing.

269
00:34:11,917 --> 00:34:14,417
什么都没有。
No nothing.

270
00:34:14,833 --> 00:34:18,500
你现在打算做什么?你会把我赶出去的，是吗?
What are you going to do now? You will kick me out, won't you?

271
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:21,500
哦，当然，毕竟这对你来说很容易。
Oh, sure, it's easy for you, after all.

272
00:34:21,583 --> 00:34:26,042
你只需要保持温暖，锁在你的小房间里祈祷。
You just need to stay warm, locked in your little room and pray.

273
00:34:27,125 --> 00:34:33,417
祈祷，祈祷，祈祷……祈祷,祈祷……
Pray, pray, pray. . . pray, pray...

274
00:34:41,042 --> 00:34:43,958
你曾经爱过谁吗?
Have you ever loved anybody?

275
00:34:44,750 --> 00:34:46,875
来吧，告诉我真相。
C'mon, tell me the truth.

276
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:49,250
好了，别害羞。
C'mon, don't be ashamed.

277
00:34:49,333 --> 00:34:52,167
你爱过真正的女人吗?
Have you ever loved a real woman?

278
00:34:57,000 --> 00:35:01,042
爱是很难的。很努力。
It's very hard to love. Very hard.

279
00:35:03,083 --> 00:35:06,292
这几乎是不可能的。
It's almost impossible.

280
00:35:10,958 --> 00:35:16,292
但你在你的讲坛上和我们谈论爱。
But you talk to us about love from your pulpit.

281
00:35:31,500 --> 00:35:33,667
这是给你的。
That's for you.

282
00:35:34,208 --> 00:35:35,833
我偷的。
I stole it.

283
00:35:35,917 --> 00:35:38,375
从你的教堂。
From your church.

284
00:35:39,333 --> 00:35:41,958
因为你要走了。
Because you're leaving.

285
00:35:53,667 --> 00:35:54,958
是的，他必须离开。
Yes, he must leave.

286
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:57,125
他必须这么做，因为他想这么做。
He must because he wants to.

287
00:35:57,208 --> 00:35:58,833
人们窃窃私语，议论纷纷。
People whisper and talk about it.

288
00:35:58,875 --> 00:36:01,458
但是他们什么也不知道，因为他们只是些可怜的家伙。
But they know nothing, as they're just poor devils.

289
00:36:01,542 --> 00:36:03,875
相反，我知道。我什么都看到了。
Instead I know. I see everything.

290
00:36:03,958 --> 00:36:07,000
不是因为上级，也不是因为共产党。
It's not because of the superiors or or even of the communists, you know.

291
00:36:07,167 --> 00:36:09,625
事实并非如此。事实是他失去了信仰。
The truth is diffent. The truth is that he lost his faith.

292
00:36:09,708 --> 00:36:13,292
我知道牧师是怎样的人。
I do know how priests are.

293
00:36:13,333 --> 00:36:15,250
但他和其他人不一样。
But he's different from the others.

294
00:36:15,250 --> 00:36:17,958
他有胡子。喜欢我。
He has the beard. Like me.

295
00:36:17,958 --> 00:36:23,458
为什么?不是因为昨天，也不是因为今天，事实是他失去了信仰。
Why? It's not due to yesterday or today, the truth is that he lost his faith.

296
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:25,708
但我理解他。
But I understand him.

297
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,583
让我们以毛为例。
Let's take Mao for example.

298
00:36:27,875 --> 00:36:29,625
我确实对毛很感兴趣。
I'm interested in Mao, indeed.

299
00:36:29,667 --> 00:36:31,000
我亲中。同意了。
I'm pro-Chinese. Agreed.

300
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,333
但我留在这里。
But I stay here.

301
00:36:32,417 --> 00:36:35,292
我是一名牧师，为教会服务。
I'm a sacriston and serve the church.

302
00:36:35,375 --> 00:36:37,208
再见。
Goodbye.

303
00:36:41,125 --> 00:36:43,250
再见。
Goodbye.

304
00:36:51,958 --> 00:36:53,250
再见,爸爸。
Goodbye, Father.

305
00:36:53,250 --> 00:36:56,458
父亲，你就这样走了?这对我们所有人来说都是一个巨大的悲伤。
Father, you go away like this? It's a big sorrow for all of us.

306
00:37:01,917 --> 00:37:03,000
再见，我的儿子。
Goodbye, my son.

307
00:37:03,417 --> 00:37:07,042
快点回来。你一直都很好。
Come back soon. You've been so good.

308
00:37:13,208 --> 00:37:16,417
再见,爸爸。
Goodbye, Father.

309
00:37:21,208 --> 00:37:24,417
再见,爸爸。祝你旅途愉快。
Goodbye, Father. Have a good trip.

310
00:37:29,792 --> 00:37:32,583
别忘了我们，父亲。
Do not forget about us, Father.

311
00:38:23,250 --> 00:38:24,667
你又在忙什么?
What are you up to again?

312
00:38:24,750 --> 00:38:26,917
你想从我这里得到什么?
What do you want from me?

313
00:38:30,792 --> 00:38:33,458
别烦我!
Leave me alone!

314
00:38:33,708 --> 00:38:35,042
停止它!
Stop it!

315
00:38:35,042 --> 00:38:37,875
我再也受不了了!
I can't take it anymore!

316
00:38:44,875 --> 00:38:48,333
说实话，我对它也不满意。
To be honest, I haven't been happy with it either.

317
00:38:48,792 --> 00:38:50,750
你知道，我太老了。
You know, I'm too old.

318
00:38:50,875 --> 00:38:54,167
这是一个让人无法满足的教区。
It's a parish which gives no satisfaction.

319
00:38:54,208 --> 00:38:56,000
几个人，周围没人。
A few people, nobody all round.

320
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:57,875
只有岛上的老监狱……
Only the old prison in the isle...

321
00:38:57,917 --> 00:39:00,083
…你偶尔会去的地方。
...where you go every once in a while.

322
00:39:00,125 --> 00:39:02,000
你知道，这很可悲。-真遗憾。
It's sad, you know. - What a pity.

323
00:39:02,042 --> 00:39:03,958
你会习惯的。
You'll get used to that.

324
00:39:04,042 --> 00:39:05,750
另一方面，游客会来的。
Tourists will come, on the other hand.

325
00:39:05,750 --> 00:39:09,667
他们来了，吃了，拍了照，买了汽油，然后又走了。
They come, eat, take pictures, get petrol and leave again.

326
00:39:09,708 --> 00:39:11,250
他们很匆忙。
They are in a hurry.

327
00:39:11,250 --> 00:39:13,083
现在每个人都很着急。
Everyone's in a hurry by now.

328
00:39:13,167 --> 00:39:14,708
还有教会。
Also the Church.

329
00:39:14,792 --> 00:39:18,250
加油站。教会服务。
Service station. Service Church.

330
00:39:18,958 --> 00:39:22,833
是的，离婚，独身，抗议。
Yes, divorce, celibacy, protest.

331
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:26,417
左翼和右翼牧师。
Left-wing and right-wing priests.

332
00:39:27,583 --> 00:39:30,208
理想危机。
Crisis of ideals.

333
00:39:35,125 --> 00:39:36,875
你需要跟上节奏。
You need to keep the pace.

334
00:39:36,917 --> 00:39:39,167
等一会儿。我给你看样东西。
Wait for a while. I'll show you something.

335
00:40:15,792 --> 00:40:19,750
你觉得呢?一个超现代和自动化的教堂。
What do you think? An ultra-modern and automatic church.

336
00:40:22,083 --> 00:40:24,583
你不会发现它比我更糟。
You won't find it worse than me.

337
00:40:34,083 --> 00:40:37,000
我就是不明白为什么人们跑得那么快。
I just can't get why people are running so fast.

338
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:42,375
看那边，每天至少发生两起车祸。
Look over there: at least two car accidents occur every day.

339
00:40:43,458 --> 00:40:45,958
还有很多新的交通标志已经安装好了。
And to say that many new traffic signs have been installed.

340
00:40:46,833 --> 00:40:49,250
我去为他们祝福。
I went and blessed them.

341
00:40:49,625 --> 00:40:52,042
这是没有用的。
It was useless.

342
00:40:52,083 --> 00:40:54,833
他们像疯了一样不停地跑。
They keep on running like mad.

343
00:40:55,708 --> 00:40:58,583
速度，速度，速度……
Speed, speed, speed...

344
00:40:59,250 --> 00:41:02,458
谁知道大家都跑到哪里去了?
Who knows where everyone's running?

345
00:41:53,833 --> 00:41:58,167
我的灵魂不要列在罪人之列，我的性命不要列在流人血的人之列
<i>Let not my soul be numbered among sinners or my life among men of blood.</i>

346
00:41:58,250 --> 00:42:02,458
他们的手中是邪恶的阴谋，他们的右手拿着金钱
<i>In whose hands are evil designs, and whose right hands take money.</i>

347
00:42:02,708 --> 00:42:08,458
至于我，却要照我所行的正直而行。求你救我，怜恤我
<i>But as for me, I'll go on in my upright ways: be my saviour and have mercy on me.</i>

348
00:46:50,542 --> 00:46:53,333
这条船出租吗?
Is this boat for rent?

349
00:46:54,708 --> 00:46:56,833
我要去钓鱼。
I need to go fishing.

350
00:46:58,792 --> 00:47:02,750
好吧，你喜欢去哪儿就去哪儿。对我来说也是一样。
Well, go wherever you like. It's the same for me.

351
00:47:05,292 --> 00:47:07,500
但它不适合我。
But it's not for me.

352
00:47:07,583 --> 00:47:09,625
我不会打扰你的。
I won't bother you.

353
00:47:17,875 --> 00:47:20,542
我们走吧?
Shall we go?

354
00:48:41,292 --> 00:48:43,583
我们一定要走远吗?
Must we get far?

355
00:48:43,750 --> 00:48:45,792
你能划多久?
How long can you row?

356
00:48:46,667 --> 00:48:49,875
慢慢地直到黄昏。
Slowly even till dusk.

357
00:48:51,042 --> 00:48:54,708
我只是需要时不时地休息一下。
I just need to get some rest from time to time.

358
00:49:00,583 --> 00:49:03,583
你知道从来没有女人上过这艘船吗?
Do you know that no woman has ever been on this boat?

359
00:49:03,583 --> 00:49:05,750
这种事从没发生在我身上。
It never happened to me.

360
00:49:06,292 --> 00:49:08,458
只有鱼。
Only fishes.

361
00:49:08,667 --> 00:49:10,792
很奇怪，不是吗?
It's strange, isn't it?

362
00:49:10,792 --> 00:49:13,625
其实并不奇怪。
Not so strange, actually.

363
00:49:15,583 --> 00:49:17,625
时代变了。
Times have changed.

364
00:49:18,292 --> 00:49:20,708
现在鱼相当稀少。
Fish is pretty scarce by now.

365
00:49:21,542 --> 00:49:23,792
渔民也是如此。
The same goes for fishermen too.

366
00:49:25,375 --> 00:49:27,792
你得将就一下。
You have to make do.

367
00:49:30,375 --> 00:49:32,792
你会睡吗?
Will you sleep?

368
00:49:42,833 --> 00:49:45,708
去做吧。
Go ahead.

369
00:49:46,583 --> 00:49:50,792
一个人不能一边划船一边说话。
One can't row and speak at the same time.

370
00:49:52,667 --> 00:49:54,750
一个人会累的。
One will get tired.

371
00:49:56,458 --> 00:49:58,667
所以保持安静。
So keep quiet.

372
00:50:02,042 --> 00:50:04,750
我们还得再往前走一点吗?
Do we have to keep going a little bit further?

373
00:50:07,250 --> 00:50:09,792
我们还得再往前走一点吗?
Do we have to keep going a little bit further?

374
00:50:26,708 --> 00:50:29,333
你不是本地人吧?
You're not from around here, are you?

375
00:50:34,750 --> 00:50:36,958
我逃脱了。
I escaped.

376
00:50:39,083 --> 00:50:41,792
从谁?
From whom?

377
00:50:43,583 --> 00:50:46,292
我逃离了所有人。
I escaped from everybody.

378
00:50:46,667 --> 00:50:49,417
或者说几乎每个人都有。
Or almost from everybody.

379
00:50:52,375 --> 00:50:54,750
你是谁?
Who are you?

380
00:50:57,167 --> 00:51:00,750
假设我现在扮演的是渔夫。
Let's say that I'm playing the fisherman right now.

381
00:51:02,500 --> 00:51:05,792
你在玩什么把戏?
What are you playing at?

382
00:51:33,250 --> 00:51:36,000
不要闭上眼睛。
Do not close your eyes.

383
00:51:38,333 --> 00:51:41,542
不要闭上眼睛……
Do not close your eyes...

384
00:51:51,000 --> 00:51:54,542
不…不要关闭…
No... do not close...

385
00:52:47,208 --> 00:52:48,917
再次见到我你高兴吗，父亲?
Are you happy to see me again, Father?

386
00:52:50,417 --> 00:52:52,500
我会说你是。
I'd say you're.

387
00:52:52,833 --> 00:52:54,708
不，你错了。
No, you're wrong.

388
00:52:54,792 --> 00:52:57,792
我已经告诉过你，我帮不了你。
I've already told you I can do nothing for you.

389
00:52:57,917 --> 00:53:01,333
你来是不对的。
It was wrong of you to come.

390
00:53:01,542 --> 00:53:04,542
如果我想认罪呢?
What if I would like to confess?

391
00:53:05,500 --> 00:53:10,042
我承认那些改过自新并希望得到宽恕的人……
I confess those who are reformed and want to be forgiven...

392
00:53:10,042 --> 00:53:13,125
…而不是那些只想找个共犯的人。
...not those only looking for a partner in their sins.

393
00:53:13,292 --> 00:53:16,583
但你得听我说，神父。
But you have to listen to me, Father.

394
00:53:17,875 --> 00:53:20,708
我听了很多像你这样的女人的忏悔……
I listened to the confessions by many women like you...

395
00:53:21,042 --> 00:53:25,333
…女人感到孤独、被抛弃……
...women feeling alone, abandoned, ...

396
00:53:25,500 --> 00:53:29,625
…被剥削，绝望，无法活下去。
...exploited, hopeless, unable to keep on living.

397
00:53:31,333 --> 00:53:35,083
你觉得自己是个特例，和其他人一样。
And you think you're a special case, just like the others.

398
00:53:36,125 --> 00:53:37,375
你乐于受苦。
You're happy to suffer.

399
00:53:37,375 --> 00:53:41,792
悲伤让你觉得自己很重要，很独特。
Sorrow makes you feel important and unique.

400
00:53:42,500 --> 00:53:44,250
试着诚实一点。
Try to be honest.

401
00:53:45,292 --> 00:53:47,667
你怕我。
You're afraid of me.

402
00:53:47,958 --> 00:53:49,625
你为什么要从我身边跑开?
Why are you running away from me?

403
00:53:49,667 --> 00:53:52,333
你为什么要欺骗自己?
Why are you deceiving yourself?

404
00:53:54,125 --> 00:53:57,792
你知道你对我有多重要吗?
Are you aware of how important you're for me?

405
00:53:58,000 --> 00:54:00,208
我和你在一起变得平和?
That I'm becoming peaceful together with you?

406
00:54:00,292 --> 00:54:02,708
我正在忘记我的过去。
And I'm forgetting my past.

407
00:54:03,625 --> 00:54:06,625
你知道，我非常敬重你。你相信我吗，父亲?
I hold you in such high esteem, you know. Do you believe me, Father?

408
00:54:06,708 --> 00:54:11,792
他们教会我相信。我得说你的感受与我无关。
They taught me to believe. I must say that your feelings don't concern me.

409
00:54:12,500 --> 00:54:17,000
你很清楚我不得不离开多少亲爱的朋友。我爱的人。
You know well how many dear friends I had to leave. People I really loved.

410
00:54:17,042 --> 00:54:21,333
但我是被迫这样做的，因为我不能再继续撒谎了!
But I was forced to do that, as I no longer could keep on lying!

411
00:54:21,500 --> 00:54:23,417
我必须重新找回自我。
I have to find myself again.

412
00:54:23,458 --> 00:54:26,708
我不能给任何人任何东西!
And I can't give anyone anything!

413
00:54:26,833 --> 00:54:29,125
不，这不是真的。
No, it's not true.

414
00:54:29,167 --> 00:54:33,208
你来这里不是为了重新找回自我，而是为了逃避真实的自己。
You aren't here to find yourself again, but to escape from what you're.

415
00:54:33,333 --> 00:54:35,000
为了躲避自己……
To hide from yourself...

416
00:54:35,042 --> 00:54:37,833
…因为你不想存在!
...because you'd like not to exist!

417
00:54:39,792 --> 00:54:42,083
我们永远不可能相互理解。
It will be never possible that we understand each other.

418
00:54:42,167 --> 00:54:44,917
你是女人，我是牧师。
You're a woman and I'm a priest.

419
00:54:44,958 --> 00:54:48,083
不，不是为了这个。
No, it's not for this.

420
00:54:49,292 --> 00:54:52,958
我们不会因为我是女人就互相理解……
We won't understand each other just because I'm a woman...

421
00:54:53,083 --> 00:54:55,583
…而你是个男人。
...and you a man.

422
00:54:56,750 --> 00:54:59,208
没什么好说的了。
There's nothing else to say.

423
00:54:59,458 --> 00:55:01,792
我什么都说了，什么也看不见了。
I've said everything and can't see anything else.

424
00:55:01,875 --> 00:55:05,542
像这样继续。
Go ahead like this.

425
00:55:05,583 --> 00:55:08,708
就像你一直做的那样。
Like you've been doing so far.

426
00:55:08,875 --> 00:55:13,542
足够了。我看不见了。现在我累了。
Enough. I can't see anymore. Now I'm tired.

427
00:55:13,792 --> 00:55:16,958
你也是。
And you too.

428
00:56:43,708 --> 00:56:45,125
我打扰你了吗?
Am I bothering you?

429
00:56:45,208 --> 00:56:47,083
你在祈祷吗?
We re you praying?

430
00:56:47,167 --> 00:56:49,292
不，我只是在想。
No, just thinking.

431
00:56:49,292 --> 00:56:52,083
跪着?
On your knees?

432
00:56:52,958 --> 00:56:57,000
多年来我一直跪着祈祷。
I've been always praying on my knees for years.

433
00:57:00,000 --> 00:57:02,250
但有时我停止祈祷。
But I stopped praying sometimes.

434
00:57:02,417 --> 00:57:04,208
那时我开始思考。
And I was starting to think at that point.

435
00:57:04,583 --> 00:57:08,833
所以现在，即使我只想思考，我也得跪下来。
So now, even if I only want to think, I've to go down on my knees.

436
00:57:11,208 --> 00:57:13,958
你在想我吗，父亲?
Were you thinking about me, Father?

437
00:57:20,250 --> 00:57:22,625
小心，离开那里，你会摔倒的。
Careful, away from there, you might fall down.

438
00:57:28,958 --> 00:57:31,125
再说一遍。
Say it again.

439
00:57:32,458 --> 00:57:34,958
以同样的方式。
In the same way.

440
00:57:36,708 --> 00:57:38,833
小心。
Careful.

441
00:57:40,375 --> 00:57:43,250
远离那里。
Away from there.

442
00:57:44,667 --> 00:57:47,292
你可能会摔倒。
You might fall down.

443
00:57:50,417 --> 00:57:53,250
你很好。
You're good.

444
00:57:53,625 --> 00:57:56,208
你在等我，对吧?
You were waiting for me, weren't you?

445
00:57:56,833 --> 00:57:58,792
来吧，说出来。
C'mon, say it.

446
00:58:04,000 --> 00:58:05,917
愿平安与你同在。
The peace be with you.

447
00:58:05,958 --> 00:58:08,042
还有你。
And also with you.

448
00:58:29,542 --> 00:58:33,208
你相信看手相的人吗?
Do you believe in palmists?

449
00:58:33,667 --> 00:58:36,292
当我还是个孩子的时候……
When I was a child...

450
00:58:36,333 --> 00:58:38,417
…一个吉卜赛女人向我母亲预言有一天……
...a gypsy woman predicted to my mother that one day...

451
00:58:38,417 --> 00:58:41,208
…我会变得富有。
...I would become rich.

452
00:58:41,583 --> 00:58:44,542
很富有。很多钱。
Very rich. Lots of money.

453
00:58:47,708 --> 00:58:49,833
真是个错误。
What a mistake.

454
00:58:50,167 --> 00:58:52,292
所以，从那时起……
So, since that time...

455
00:58:52,792 --> 00:58:55,208
…我不再相信这些东西了。
...I haven't believed in these things anymore.

456
00:58:56,500 --> 00:58:58,000
相反，我相信。
I believe, instead.

457
00:58:58,167 --> 00:59:00,417
我相信一切。
I believe in everything.

458
00:59:00,583 --> 00:59:04,625
我相信黑猫，相信咖啡桌被撞……
I believe in a black cat, in a coffee table being hit...

459
00:59:05,292 --> 00:59:07,208
…我害怕吸血鬼
...and I'm afraid of vampires.

460
00:59:07,292 --> 00:59:11,250
你什么也看不懂，它们只是一些混乱的线条。
There's nothing you can understand there, they are only confused lines.

461
00:59:11,417 --> 00:59:14,208
这不是真的。
That's not true.

462
00:59:14,583 --> 00:59:16,292
不过那个吉普赛女人说得对。
Oh, that gypsy woman was right, though.

463
00:59:16,375 --> 00:59:19,917
我也看到了丰富，非常丰富。
I also see richness, a great richness.

464
00:59:20,958 --> 00:59:23,250
这是你的救命稻草。
Here's your lifeline.

465
00:59:23,250 --> 00:59:25,750
这是幸福线。
This is the line of happiness.

466
00:59:25,833 --> 00:59:29,917
幸福的线真的很深。
The line of happiness is really very deep.

467
00:59:30,000 --> 00:59:33,208
这是心线。
And that's the line of heart.

468
00:59:33,417 --> 00:59:39,083
心的那一段很长很长。
The one of heart is very very long.

469
00:59:39,792 --> 00:59:45,125
看，它往下，往下，往下……
See, it goes down, down, down...

470
00:59:45,250 --> 00:59:47,125
…直到这里。
...until here.

471
00:59:55,292 --> 00:59:56,458
你知道这句谚语吗?
Do you know this saying?

472
00:59:56,458 --> 01:00:00,250
智慧是你的姐妹，谨慎是你的朋友。
Wisdom be your sister and prudence your friend.

473
01:00:34,833 --> 01:00:38,125
我们为什么要躲起来?
Why do we have to hide?

474
01:00:39,083 --> 01:00:41,833
有时候很有趣。
It's funny sometimes.

475
01:02:04,208 --> 01:02:05,625
你为什么把我带到这里来?
Why have you brought me just here?

476
01:02:05,750 --> 01:02:08,125
过来一下。
Come here a minute.

477
01:02:20,708 --> 01:02:22,250
那又怎样?
So what?

478
01:02:22,292 --> 01:02:24,208
我想带你看看我出生的地方。
I wanted to show you where I was born.

479
01:02:24,250 --> 01:02:26,000
在罗马斗兽场?
At the Colosseum?

480
01:02:26,875 --> 01:02:29,792
不，在那边。你能看到那个十字路口吗?
No, over there. Can you see that crossroads?

481
01:02:30,208 --> 01:02:31,458
没有,在哪里?在右边?
No, where? On the right?

482
01:02:31,583 --> 01:02:34,292
不，左边第二个。——是的。
No, the second one on the left. - Yes.

483
01:02:54,375 --> 01:02:58,292
晚上好。你想吃什么?
Good evening. What do you want to eat?

484
01:02:59,417 --> 01:03:02,583
那你今晚就吃我给你带来的吧。
Well, so you'll eat what I bring you this evening.

485
01:03:02,958 --> 01:03:06,292
我要做点好吃的，真正的特色菜。
I'll give something tasty, a true speciality.

486
01:03:06,292 --> 01:03:09,250
专为情侣做的菜。
A dish made especially for lovers.

487
01:03:10,792 --> 01:03:15,958
要不要来点好吃的，真正的特色菜，为情侣特制的菜?
Will you have something tasty, a true speciality, a special dish for lovers?

488
01:03:18,750 --> 01:03:20,500
你为什么那么固执?
Why were you so stubborn?

489
01:03:20,833 --> 01:03:23,250
你穿那条裙子真好看。
You look great in that dress.

490
01:03:23,458 --> 01:03:26,292
我很喜欢你。
I like you so much.

491
01:03:26,958 --> 01:03:30,250
我也很高兴今晚能来到这里。
I'm also very happy to be here tonight.

492
01:03:32,708 --> 01:03:35,292
我又饿又渴。
I'm hungry and thirsty.

493
01:03:35,292 --> 01:03:39,250
我也很高兴我不用在加油站吃饭。
I'm also very happy that I don't have to eat at the service station.

494
01:03:44,542 --> 01:03:46,375
有什么事吗?
What's up?

495
01:03:46,375 --> 01:03:49,292
不要回头。
Do not turn around.

496
01:03:58,167 --> 01:04:00,292
谁在那里？
Who's there?

497
01:04:01,667 --> 01:04:04,292
没关系。
It doesn't matter.

498
01:04:31,375 --> 01:04:33,458
你很好。
You're good.

499
01:04:33,500 --> 01:04:35,917
我们走吧。
Let's go.

500
01:05:08,500 --> 01:05:10,625
我们还没有付帐。
We haven't paid the bill.

501
01:05:10,625 --> 01:05:13,208
我们下次再去。
We shall go there another time.

502
01:06:38,208 --> 01:06:40,250
她死了。
She's dead.

503
01:07:05,167 --> 01:07:07,333
你是牧师吗?
Are you a priest?

504
01:07:11,667 --> 01:07:14,250
不，我不是。
No, I'm not.

505
01:07:50,083 --> 01:07:53,292
把车开到车库去。
Take the car to the garage.

506
01:07:56,958 --> 01:07:59,250
然后上来。
Then come up.

507
01:09:17,875 --> 01:09:20,292
转身……
Turn around...

508
01:09:20,792 --> 01:09:23,292
看着我……
Look at me...

509
01:09:23,333 --> 01:09:26,292
不要害怕……
Don't be afraid...

510
01:09:30,042 --> 01:09:32,292
转身……
Turn around...

511
01:09:32,542 --> 01:09:34,958
看着我……
Look at me...

512
01:09:35,000 --> 01:09:37,292
不要害怕……
Don't be afraid...

513
01:09:37,542 --> 01:09:40,292
不要害怕……
Don't be afraid...

514
01:09:41,500 --> 01:09:46,292
你不必……
Yo don't have to...

515
01:10:08,125 --> 01:10:09,750
太迟了。
It's too late.

516
01:10:09,875 --> 01:10:12,292
我不再年轻了。
I'm not young anymore.

517
01:10:13,375 --> 01:10:16,917
我现在已经无法改变我的生活了。
I can no longer change my life by now.

518
01:10:19,250 --> 01:10:22,917
我每天晚上都感到恐惧和痛苦。
I'm always feeling fear and anguish every night.

519
01:10:23,208 --> 01:10:24,750
一切都让我害怕。
Everything scares me.

520
01:10:24,875 --> 01:10:27,208
不，不是所有的，但是……
No, not everything, but...

521
01:10:29,000 --> 01:10:30,750
…事情将如何发展，直到……
...how things will be till...

522
01:10:30,750 --> 01:10:36,292
