There's no way out.

524
01:11:33,167 --> 01:11:34,500
你真漂亮。
You're so beautiful.

525
01:11:34,542 --> 01:11:39,125
喜欢总是。就像往常一样，你突然出现了。
Like always. And, like always, you come up all of a sudden.

526
01:11:39,292 --> 01:11:40,667
