当我需要的时候，我会问你的。
When I need it, I will ask you.

531
01:11:52,917 --> 01:11:54,750
很好。
Very well.

532
01:11:54,833 --> 01:11:58,250
如果不是为了钱，那又怎样?
And if it's not about the money, so what?

533
01:12:02,125 --> 01:12:06,208
不，我只是想让你下定决心同意我离婚。
No, I just want you to make up your mind and grant me a divorce.

534
01:12:08,208 --> 01:12:10,750
毕竟，这对你来说只是个价格问题。
It's just a matter of a price for you, after all.

535
01:12:10,875 --> 01:12:14,208
当然!只是价格的问题。
Sure! Just a matter of a price.

536
01:12:14,250 --> 01:12:18,917
你让我付出了很多，所以我没有理由要失去你。
You has cost me a lot, so there's no reason why I'd have to lose you.

537
01:12:19,000 --> 01:12:22,292
不，一件珍贵的东西不能就这样浪费掉。
No, a precious object is not to be wasted like that.

538
01:12:22,292 --> 01:12:25,292
此外，你必须考虑到我对你的感觉，即使是现在。
Moreover, you must consider what I feel for you, even now.

539
01:12:25,333 --> 01:12:28,292
拜托，拜托。
Please, come on.

540
01:12:33,375 --> 01:12:39,208
不管怎样，这还不是全部。
That's not all, anyway.

541
01:12:40,042 --> 01:12:41,833
还有另一个原因。
There's another reason.

542
01:12:41,917 --> 01:12:45,167
当我遇见你的时候，你是我的替补。
When I met you, you were a third string.

543
01:12:45,167 --> 01:12:47,292
我是说你什么都不是。
I mean you were nothing.

544
01:12:47,833 --> 01:12:50,458
我把你介绍给重要人物。
I've introduced you to important people.

545
01:12:50,458 --> 01:12:53,292
我用我的爱创造了你……
I've made you with my love...

546
01:12:53,875 --> 01:12:56,458
…还有我的钱。
...and with my money.

547
01:12:56,500 --> 01:12:59,000
为什么?这不是真的吗?
Why? Isn't that true?

548
01:13:00,750 --> 01:13:04,208
这就是我恨你的原因，你很清楚。
That's just why I hate you and you know it very well.

549
01:13:04,583 --> 01:13:07,042
是这个原因吗?真的吗?
Is this the reason? Really?

550
01:13:07,042 --> 01:13:09,000
是的，就是这样。
Yes, that's it.

551
01:13:10,042 --> 01:13:12,250
你从没想过把我看得很高。
You never wanted to think highly of me.

552
01:13:12,583 --> 01:13:15,292
我一直都是你的玩具。
I've always been a toy for you.

553
01:13:15,792 --> 01:13:18,208
因为我喜欢你那样。
Because I liked you like that.

554
01:13:22,125 --> 01:13:24,250
你真是无与伦比。
You're really inimitable.

555
01:13:26,500 --> 01:13:29,292
那你有什么建议?
Well, what are you proposing?

556
01:13:29,833 --> 01:13:32,542
我知道我们有进展了。
I see that now we're getting somewhere.

557
01:13:33,667 --> 01:13:37,208
好吧，我的建议是。
Well, here's my proposition.

558
01:13:37,542 --> 01:13:39,875
我们同意离婚。
We will agree with the divorce.

559
01:13:39,917 --> 01:13:43,292
唯一的条件是你要成为我的爱人。
The only condition is that you'll become my lover.

560
01:13:44,000 --> 01:13:45,917
现在你是我的妻子……
Now you're my wife...

561
01:13:46,167 --> 01:13:48,708
…你有很多情人。
...you have got many lovers.

562
01:13:48,875 --> 01:13:51,292
然后你就会成为另一个男人的妻子，但是……
Then you'll be the wife of another man but...

563
01:13:51,917 --> 01:13:53,417
…你要和我睡。
...you will sleep with me.

564
01:13:54,917 --> 01:13:56,417
这很合理，不是吗?
It's reasonable, isn't it?

565
01:13:58,250 --> 01:14:00,292
你真让我恶心。
You make me sick.

566
01:14:03,708 --> 01:14:07,292
但我爱你……代替。
But I love you... instead.

567
01:14:14,542 --> 01:14:17,667
因为男人不是由女人而来的
<i>For man did not come from woman...</i>

568
01:14:17,667 --> 01:14:20,708
<我>…但是女人来自男人。</i>
<i>...but woman from man.</i>

569
01:14:20,708 --> 01:14:23,875
男人也不是为女人而创造的，</i>…
<i>Nor was man created for woman,</i> ...

570
01:14:23,958 --> 01:14:26,958
<我>…但是女人对男人。</i>
<i>...but woman for man.</i>

571
01:14:27,625 --> 01:14:33,500
因此，女人的头上应该有一个男人权威的标志，</i>…
<i>Hence a woman should have a sign of authority of man on her head,</i> ...

572
01:14:33,500 --> 01:14:37,125
<我>…因为天使。</i>
<i>...because of the angels.</i>

573
01:14:37,167 --> 01:14:42,083
另一方面，女人也不是独立于男人之外的
<i>On the other hand, woman is not independent of man...</i>

574
01:14:42,083 --> 01:14:45,875
<我>…或在主里的男人或女人。</i>
<i>...or man of woman in the Lord.</i>

575
01:14:45,958 --> 01:14:48,208
因为正如女人是从男人而来的
<i>For just as woman came from man...</i>

576
01:14:48,208 --> 01:14:51,083
<我>…所以男人是由女人所生的
<i>...so man is born of woman.</i>

577
01:14:56,708 --> 01:15:00,250
万物都是出于神
<i>And all things are from God.</i>

578
01:15:02,125 --> 01:15:03,708
你能划多久?
How long can you row?

579
01:15:03,833 --> 01:15:06,292
我不知道。
I don't know.

580
01:15:14,542 --> 01:15:18,292
我打赌这是圣经里的话。
I bet it was a quote from the Bible.

581
01:15:19,708 --> 01:15:23,292
圣保罗写给哥林多人的第一封信。
From St. Paul's First Letter to the Corinthians.

582
01:15:23,292 --> 01:15:26,292
就是这样。
That's it.

583
01:15:29,042 --> 01:15:31,208
再见!
Goodbye!

584
