我忘了告诉你我游泳游得很好。
I forgot to tell you that I'm a very good swimmer.

585
01:19:31,458 --> 01:19:33,708
今天早上刚抓到的。
Just caught this morning.

586
01:19:33,708 --> 01:19:37,208
是的，就像我以前在市场上买的鱼一样。
Yes, like the fish I use to buy at the market.

587
01:19:44,375 --> 01:19:47,208
你知道，这里很好。
It's nice here, you know.

588
01:19:47,500 --> 01:19:51,250
你打算在这间公寓里住很长时间吗?
Are you going to stay in this apartment for a long time?

589
01:19:53,500 --> 01:19:55,250
我必须再见到你。-你疯了!
I had to see you again. - You crazy!

590
01:19:55,250 --> 01:19:56,292
别烦我。
Leave me alone.

591
01:19:56,292 --> 01:19:58,417
你在我的脑海里挥之不去。
You're stuck in my head.

592
01:19:58,417 --> 01:20:00,125
事情本不必这样结束的……
It didn't have to end like this...

593
01:20:00,125 --> 01:20:01,833
到这里来。
Come here.

594
01:20:03,792 --> 01:20:05,833
走开!-别动。
Go away! - Stay still.

595
01:20:05,833 --> 01:20:08,000
我再也不想了!- - - - - -什么? !
I no longer want to! - What?!

596
01:20:08,000 --> 01:20:11,167
我不想!——安静。
I don't want to! - Quiet.

597
01:20:13,500 --> 01:20:16,250
我说不!
I said no!

598
01:21:03,583 --> 01:21:06,292
她也是你的女人吗?
Is she your woman too?

599
01:21:09,500 --> 01:21:13,292
我，你和她。所以我们有三个人。
Me, you and her. Hence there's three of us.

600
01:21:16,208 --> 01:21:19,792
你这个笨蛋!白痴!
You dumb ass! Idiot!

601
01:21:19,875 --> 01:21:23,292
我已经和她睡过了!她想要我。
I've been already sleeping with her! She wanted me.

602
01:21:23,375 --> 01:21:25,708
你明白吗?
Do you understand that?

603
01:21:25,708 --> 01:21:28,708
她想要我!我都不用问她。
She wanted me! I didn't even have to ask her.

604
01:21:29,125 --> 01:21:31,292
她是惊人的。
She's amazing.

605
01:21:31,708 --> 01:21:34,292
她像女神一样做爱。
She makes love like a goddess.

606
01:21:43,000 --> 01:21:45,250
你这个哭哭啼啼的绿帽子。
You crying cuckold.

607
01:21:50,833 --> 01:21:53,042
他是对的。
He's right.

608
01:21:53,167 --> 01:21:57,000
都是你的错。邪恶在你身上，你不想改变。
It's your fault. Evil is in you and you don't want to change.

609
01:21:57,042 --> 01:21:58,625
所以像你这样的女人永远不想改变!
So women like you never want to change!

610
01:21:58,625 --> 01:22:01,292
你们都是一样的!都一样!
You are all the same! All the same!

611
01:23:43,458 --> 01:23:46,292
我跟踪你来不是因为你说得对。
I didn't follow you here because you're right.

612
01:23:46,417 --> 01:23:48,542
不是那样的。
It's not like that.

613
01:23:48,708 --> 01:23:51,000
看着我。
Look at me.

614
01:23:54,750 --> 01:23:57,167
好吧。
All right.

615
01:23:59,125 --> 01:24:01,208
所以我在这里等你。
So I'll wait for you here.

616
01:24:04,958 --> 01:24:09,250
欢迎您,爸爸。
Welcome, Father.

617
01:24:10,000 --> 01:24:12,083
进来。
Come in.

618
01:25:42,417 --> 01:25:45,250
嘿!听。
Hey! Listen.

619
01:25:45,333 --> 01:25:48,167
你有烟吗?
Do you have a cigarette?

620
01:26:01,917 --> 01:26:05,417
美丽的…
Beautiful...

621
01:26:06,500 --> 01:26:09,167
不，别走。
No, don't go away.

622
01:26:11,583 --> 01:26:15,917
让我看看。-放开我!
Let me see it. - Let me go!

623
01:26:17,417 --> 01:26:20,000
等待。——不!
Wait. - No!

624
01:26:20,250 --> 01:26:23,042
你要去哪里?——够了!
Where are you going? - Enough!

625
01:26:23,417 --> 01:26:26,042
等等!你要去哪里?
Wait! Where are you going?

626
01:26:27,792 --> 01:26:29,875
到这里来。
Come here.

627
01:26:59,250 --> 01:27:01,333
放开我!
Let me go!

628
01:27:30,750 --> 01:27:32,125
你在干什么，神父?
What are you doing, Father?

629
01:27:32,417 --> 01:27:35,500
把钥匙还给我。来吧!
Give back the keys. Come on!

630
01:28:17,375 --> 01:28:19,333
那是监狱里最古老的地方。
That's the oldest part of the prison.

631
01:28:19,500 --> 01:28:21,750
它已经很多年没有被使用了。
It's hasn't been used for many years now.

632
01:28:22,208 --> 01:28:24,500
总有一天它会崩溃。
It will collapse one day.

633
01:28:24,667 --> 01:28:26,708
被判无期徒刑的囚犯住在这里。
Life sentenced prisoners stay here.

634
01:28:46,792 --> 01:28:49,792
原谅我。这几天我想了很多。
Forgive me. I've been doing a lot of thinking these past few days.

635
01:28:50,000 --> 01:28:52,625
现在我要告诉你…
And now I have to tell you that...

636
01:28:54,583 --> 01:28:58,667
什么也别说。我知道这对你来说不可能。
Don't say anything. I know it's impossible for you.

637
01:28:59,833 --> 01:29:04,417
当你在讲坛上讲话时，你可以向你的奉献者谈论爱。
You can talk about love to your devotees, when speaking from the pulpit.

638
01:29:05,667 --> 01:29:08,250
但你不能对一个单身女人这么说。
But you can't tell that to a single woman.

639
01:29:12,292 --> 01:29:14,292
等待。
Wait.

640
01:29:14,375 --> 01:29:17,792
等一下。呆着别动!
Wait for a moment. Stay still!

641
01:29:27,542 --> 01:29:31,542
这很简单。那么简单。
It's so easy. So simple.

642
01:29:32,042 --> 01:29:35,542
每天都有数以百万计的人对彼此说这句话。
Millions of people say that to each other every day.

643
01:29:43,625 --> 01:29:46,208
不，我不能代替你说。
No, I can't say that instead of you.

644
01:29:46,375 --> 01:29:49,292
你必须这么说。
You have to say that.

645
01:30:28,500 --> 01:30:32,083
你找他干什么?你为什么总缠着他?放开他!
What do you seek of him? Why are you always stuck to him? Let him go!

646
01:30:32,250 --> 01:30:33,958
他不适合你!-我就是不明白。放开我!
He's not for you! - I just don't get it. Let me go!

647
01:30:33,958 --> 01:30:36,167
是的，你明白了。他是我儿子。
Yes, you do get it. He's my son.

648
01:30:36,167 --> 01:30:38,208
我和上帝的儿子，仅此而已!现在明白了吗?
My and God's son and nothing else! Got it now?

649
01:30:38,333 --> 01:30:41,375
他已经为我——他的母亲——做了牧师。他爱我。
He has become a priest for me, his mother. And he loves me.

650
01:30:41,792 --> 01:30:45,542
他曾经很快乐……平和快乐。
Once he was happy... Peaceful and happy.

651
01:30:45,750 --> 01:30:49,917
你为什么不放过他?我求你了。
Why don't you leave him alone? I beg you.

652
01:30:50,167 --> 01:30:56,500
小心，如果你毁了他或者你想这么做，我会杀了你，我有能力。
Beware, if you ruin him or if you want to, I'll kill you, I'm able to.

653
01:30:58,917 --> 01:31:01,667
你是个坏女人。
You're a bad woman.

654
01:31:08,125 --> 01:31:10,750
你是个坏妈妈。
And you're a bad mother.

655
01:31:51,542 --> 01:31:54,500
你会杀了我，不是吗?
You would kill me, wouldn't you?

656
01:31:54,583 --> 01:31:57,458
你是怎么猜到的?
How could you guess that?

657
01:31:57,500 --> 01:31:59,542
我了解你。
I know you.

658
01:31:59,583 --> 01:32:02,500
至少你会承认我是个听话的丈夫。
At least you'd acknowledge that I'm an obedient husband.

659
01:32:02,625 --> 01:32:05,250
你打电话给我，我就赶过来了。
You've called me and I've just rushed over here.

660
01:32:05,292 --> 01:32:08,750
你知道我差点就想你了吗?
You know that I've almost missed you?

661
01:32:19,250 --> 01:32:21,042
好吧，你愿意和我一起回去吗?
Well, will you come back with me?

662
01:32:21,125 --> 01:32:22,792
不，我不是必须成为你的爱人吗?
No, didn't I have to become your lover?

663
01:32:22,792 --> 01:32:24,708
什么时候?
When?

664
01:32:24,708 --> 01:32:27,708
即使是现在，如果你愿意。
Even now, if you want.

665
01:32:31,792 --> 01:32:33,417
我不相信你。
I don't trust you.

666
01:32:33,458 --> 01:32:36,167
我也不相信你。
I don't trust you either.

667
01:32:44,667 --> 01:32:45,917
我们要去哪里?
Well, where are we going?

668
01:32:45,958 --> 01:32:49,458
你说"在哪儿"是什么意思?当然是去你家了。
What do you mean "where"? To your place, of course.

669
01:32:49,458 --> 01:32:51,792
不是说好了吗?
Wasn't that the deal?

670
01:33:33,375 --> 01:33:37,583
哎哟!
Ouch!

671
01:33:58,583 --> 01:34:01,708
帮我一下。快。帮帮我。
Give me a hand. Quick. Help me out.

672
01:34:02,333 --> 01:34:06,792
我不能……我动不了了。
I can't... I can't move.

673
01:34:10,333 --> 01:34:12,792
你为什么只是站在那里?
Why are you just standing there?

674
01:34:13,208 --> 01:34:20,792
给别人打电话。难道你看不出我做不到吗?哎哟!该死的!
Call people or someone. Don't you see I can't make it? Ouch! Damn!

675
01:34:27,917 --> 01:34:30,292
你在干什么?哎哟!
What are you doing? Ouch!

676
01:34:30,417 --> 01:34:32,750
停止它!白痴!
Stop it! Idiot!

677
01:34:37,042 --> 01:34:39,708
寻求帮助。快点。
Ask for help. Hurry up.

678
01:34:40,833 --> 01:34:46,500
停车!做点什么!来吧!快……
Stop a car! Do something! Come on! Quick...

679
01:34:54,000 --> 01:34:56,458
你在看什么?
What are you staring at?

680
01:34:56,542 --> 01:34:59,750
走吧!快跑!
Go! Run!

681
01:35:16,833 --> 01:35:22,125
你还在等什么?难道你看不见我快死了吗?
What the hell are you waiting for? Can't you see I'm dying?

682
01:35:36,333 --> 01:35:38,750
你听不见我说话吗?
Can't you hear me?

683
01:35:43,542 --> 01:35:46,750
看看有多少血。
Look how much blood.

684
01:35:50,292 --> 01:35:52,750
多少血啊……
How much blood...

685
01:36:29,708 --> 01:36:33,042
你想要什么?我不能忏悔你。
What do you want? I can't confess you.

686
01:36:33,625 --> 01:36:35,750
等待。我杀了我丈夫。
Wait. I've killed my husband.

687
01:36:40,042 --> 01:36:44,417
我的天啊。
Oh, my God.

688
01:36:51,833 --> 01:36:54,833
我都是为了你!对我们来说!我现在自由了!
I did that for you! For us! I'm free now!

689
01:36:54,833 --> 01:36:57,000
你该死，你犯了最严重的罪……
You're damned, you committed the worst sin...

690
01:36:57,000 --> 01:36:58,250
我才不在乎呢!
I don't even care!

691
01:36:58,250 --> 01:37:00,292
别那样说，别那样说话。
Do not say that, do not talk like that.

692
01:37:00,333 --> 01:37:04,333
低下头。你能听到我说话吗?跟我念:我的错……
Bow your head. Can you hear me? Repeat after me: mea culpa...

693
01:37:04,417 --> 01:37:06,208
你就不能说点别的吗?
Can't you say anything else?

694
01:37:06,208 --> 01:37:07,875
闭嘴!不要亵渎!
Shut up! Don't blaspheme!

695
01:37:07,875 --> 01:37:10,792
我的错，我的错，我最大的错，我的错，我的错……
Mea culpa, mea culpa, mea maxima culpa, mea culpa, mea culpa...

696
01:37:10,792 --> 01:37:12,333
没用的!
It will be no use!

697
01:37:12,333 --> 01:37:13,542
求你不要折磨我。
Please, do not torment me.

698
01:37:13,542 --> 01:37:15,167
我不能赦免你。我不能原谅你。
I can't absolve you. I can't forgive you.

699
01:37:15,167 --> 01:37:16,333
我不能和你呆在一起。
I can't stay with you.

700
01:37:16,333 --> 01:37:18,583
上帝啊，宽恕我的罪过吧。
God, forgive my sins.

701
01:37:18,583 --> 01:37:20,417
你也原谅了我。
And you forgive me as well.

702
01:37:20,458 --> 01:37:22,333
主啊，在这试炼中帮助我。
Lord, help me in this trial.

703
01:37:22,333 --> 01:37:25,792
这样我就不会永远迷路了。主啊，请原谅我。
So that I won't get lost forever. Forgive me, Lord.

704
01:37:26,917 --> 01:37:30,542
主啊，听我的祷告。请不要拒绝我的帮助。
Lord, hear my prayer. Do not deny me your help.

705
01:37:30,583 --> 01:37:34,542
听我的召唤。我在这里只是短暂的客人。
Listen to my call. I'm your guest here only for a short time.

706
01:39:45,833 --> 01:39:48,667
让我们祈祷吧。
Let us pray.

707
01:39:58,708 --> 01:40:01,042
主啊，我既领受了……
Having received, o Lord...

708
01:40:01,042 --> 01:40:05,208
…救赎你的圣礼……
...the sacrament of your salvation...

709
01:40:05,250 --> 01:40:10,792
…我们恳求你，让圣母保佑我们吧。
...we beg you, let the Blessed Virgin of the Street protect us.

710
01:40:12,250 --> 01:40:16,792
我们总想留在他多情的保护下。
Under whose amorous protection we always want to stay.

711
01:40:20,792 --> 01:40:25,833
在她多情的保护下…我们总是想留下来。
Under whose amorous protection ...we always want to stay.

712
01:40:29,042 --> 01:40:34,708
在他的多情保护下，我们总是想要……
Under whose amorous protection we always want...

713
01:43:02,458 --> 01:43:05,208
你为什么不想爱我?
Why don't you want to love me?

714
01:43:05,375 --> 01:43:08,750
我爱你。就像我爱其他男人一样。
I love you. Like I love all the other men.

715
01:43:10,750 --> 01:43:12,792
你是个骗子。
You're a liar.

716
01:43:13,417 --> 01:43:16,333
你不可能以同样的方式爱每一个人。
You can't love everyone in the same way.

717
01:43:16,417 --> 01:43:20,000
你不可能像我爱你那样爱别人。
And you can't love the others in the same way I love you.

718
01:43:20,375 --> 01:43:22,792
你是亵渎神明的。
You're blasphemous.

719
01:43:37,042 --> 01:43:41,542
好的!够了!别再提这件事了。
Ok! That's enough! Let's say no more about it.

720
01:43:42,583 --> 01:43:45,083
我再也不会见你了。
Never again.

721
01:43:47,333 --> 01:43:49,583
你现在在干什么?
What are you doing now?

722
01:43:49,625 --> 01:43:50,833
我想去游泳。
I want to take a swim.

723
01:43:50,833 --> 01:43:52,500
不,请。
No, please.

724
01:43:52,500 --> 01:43:54,500
如果你怕我自杀，你也来吧。
If you're afraid I'll kill myself, you come too.

725
01:43:54,542 --> 01:43:56,375
拜托!别这么做!
Please! Don't do it!

726
01:43:56,500 --> 01:43:59,042
如果你愿意，你还是可以救我的。
You can still save me, if you want.

727
01:43:59,167 --> 01:44:01,667
你为什么不敢看我?
Why are you afraid of looking at me?

728
01:44:01,708 --> 01:44:03,708
你喝醉了。
You're drunk.

729
01:44:05,500 --> 01:44:07,750
你很可笑。
And you're ridiculous.

730
01:44:08,417 --> 01:44:14,708
你是可笑的!一个可笑的牧师!一个可笑的人!
You're ridiculous! A ridiculous priest! And a ridiculous man!

731
01:44:15,667 --> 01:44:20,667
你是可笑的!
You're ridiculous!

732
01:44:59,333 --> 01:45:02,292
做得好!来了!
Well done! Come!

733
01:45:09,583 --> 01:45:10,917
你能做到的!
You can do it!

734
01:45:11,083 --> 01:45:13,792
来吧!潜水!
Come on! Dive!

735
01:45:46,583 --> 01:45:48,583
而现在……
And now...

736
01:45:49,833 --> 01:45:52,792
现在你得告诉我真相。
Now you have to tell me the truth.

737
01:45:55,417 --> 01:45:57,708
你喜欢我吗?
Do you like me?

738
01:45:58,875 --> 01:46:01,792
很多。
A lot.

739
01:47:45,667 --> 01:47:47,792
我们离得太远了!
We're too far out!

740
01:47:48,333 --> 01:47:50,042
我们回去好吗?
Shall we head back?

741
01:47:50,042 --> 01:47:52,750
我累了。
I'm tired.

742
01:48:02,958 --> 01:48:05,750
停!
Stop!

743
01:48:11,125 --> 01:48:14,208
你能听到我说话吗?回来!
Can you hear me? Come back!

744
01:48:51,458 --> 01:48:55,167
停!回来!
Stop! Come back!

745
01:48:56,000 --> 01:48:58,792
停!
Stop!

